{"tid":1409481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【跪求推Post】女性必備！偽文青工人褲、Playsuit、內穿Bodysuit","createTime":"2019-08-04T21:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T01:42:06.000Z","uid":152123,"like":232,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"7f29f342c56281f038ef88a0543568cf2b831214","tid":1409481,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:47:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>依家就算唔發夢<br />\n出街路過都隨時成為被侵犯對象<br />\n除非自我禁足唔出街，否則女性都好難自保<br />\n大家可以考慮以下裝束<br />\n唔怕被扯高件衫嚟露Bra、除褲示眾</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一、外穿 工人褲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.topshop.com/i/TopShop/TS05P87MWBK_M_1.jpg?$w700$&amp;qlt=80\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.topshop.com%2Fi%2FTopShop%2FTS05P87MWBK_M_1.jpg%3F%24w700%24%26qlt%3D80&h=60b234b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n二、Playsuit<br />\n<img src=\"https://onepiece.imgix.net/original-slim-short-jumpsuit-black-8.jpg?w=494&amp;h=790&amp;fit=crop&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.imgix.net%2Foriginal-slim-short-jumpsuit-black-8.jpg%3Fw%3D494%26h%3D790%26fit%3Dcrop%26q%3D75&h=62037e86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdnd.lystit.com/photos/missguided/49f3862c/missguided-designer-black-Tall-Black-Lettuce-Hem-Playsuit.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdnd.lystit.com%2Fphotos%2Fmissguided%2F49f3862c%2Fmissguided-designer-black-Tall-Black-Lettuce-Hem-Playsuit.jpeg&h=5ea00b63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51TScwcyciL._UX385_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F51TScwcyciL._UX385_.jpg&h=fa2f41ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三、內穿Bodysuit (有啲bodysuit下面係有個扣 可以拆開去廁所嘅)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/jd_117999_a?qlt=80\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi8.amplience.net%2Fi%2Fjpl%2Fjd_117999_a%3Fqlt%3D80&h=115b2494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/88/3e/41/883e41560db597dd0e7fd627ade252c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F736x%2F88%2F3e%2F41%2F883e41560db597dd0e7fd627ade252c1.jpg&h=ad84bc86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>唔建議著泳衣 因為泳衣唔索汗而且緊身</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>邊度有得賣？</strong><br />\n前者周街都有，後兩者香港的確係少見，但外國非常流行，建議大家上ASOS同Amazon集運，或者去H&amp;M等外國時裝店碰下運氣<br />\ne.g.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Caracilia-Striped-Jumpsuit-Rompers-Playsuit/dp/B07F812BWW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.uk%2FCaracilia-Striped-Jumpsuit-Rompers-Playsuit%2Fdp%2FB07F812BWW&d=nzz81mtU0v8QN53TvL9Qof3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=c3db53b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.co.uk/Caracilia-Striped-Jumpsuit-Rompers-Playsuit/dp/B07F812BWW</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asos.com/asos-design/asos-design-square-neck-vest-body-in-rib-in-black/prd/11119659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asos.com%2Fasos-design%2Fasos-design-square-neck-vest-body-in-rib-in-black%2Fprd%2F11119659&d=nzz81mtU0v8QN53TvL9Qof3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=8bae7165\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.asos.com/asos-design/asos-design-square-neck-vest-body-in-rib-in-black/prd/11119659</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後希望Admin幫手宣揚一下呢個Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦希望各位巴打介紹畀你身邊嘅女性朋友同親人<br />\n我相信冇人會想自己屋企人同女朋友 行個街都被除衫示眾"},{"pid":"43e65cf4501899ea615d446541ca3c1763d8fe8a","tid":1409481,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:48:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b337f1af6770e07aa94094b1bcd085292c93c7f","tid":1409481,"uid":30268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:49:29.000Z","msg":"[啱先開錯台] 麻煩大家將天水圍女仔單野dm 畀Anne Hathaway<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1409243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1409243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"37b6b3224fb147e14416c380dd5d73338f089434","tid":1409481,"uid":152123,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:49:34.000Z","msg":"根據之前巴打嘅建議<br />\n我已經專登整合咗更多選擇畀各位女性朋友<br />\n如果大家有更好嘅提議歡迎留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660994e1dea54091f87ce4b504c57cff3efa2cdc","tid":1409481,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43e65cf4501899ea615d446541ca3c1763d8fe8a","tid":1409481,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:48:50.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:50:22.000Z","msg":"感謝"},{"pid":"082eac73ee19ce446cf93813fda82a6a51002df1","tid":1409481,"uid":149566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6z1yYmX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6z1yYmX.jpg&h=e20c9467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n罷罷罷"},{"pid":"1a440aaf9c3e34caf14bd35d9756729ac913f576","tid":1409481,"uid":63117,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:50:50.000Z","msg":"前線仲係有絲打著熱褲。。"},{"pid":"730faed338a6067eebdf82b3a1b14ed8e5d9c72f","tid":1409481,"uid":152123,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:51:26.000Z","msg":"我都係絲打<br />\n明白咁樣著一定係冇咁方便<br />\n但希望大家明白今次事件嘅嚴重性<br />\n係對女性極大嘅侮辱同埋危害<br />\n非常時期 希望大家唔好怕麻煩"},{"pid":"ed721ed73a00f2ef68e773d1ac681ea93d663da9","tid":1409481,"uid":152123,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:52:36.000Z","msg":"外穿工人褲或者playsuit 去廁所一下除曬就得<br />\n內穿bodysuit可以揀有扣嘅 好似第二幅圖咁"},{"pid":"714b0744